{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"560961f44a","title":"北京市军事管制委员会负责人谈取缔一切反动组织","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e0c801bf63","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":25,"articleId":"560961f44a","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"公安与法律","id":"53b954d860","type":"主题"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"异端思潮","id":"ca0e96a612","type":"主题"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"},{"name":"北京市军管会负责人","id":"f53890bf35","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"fd183a834c","name":"北京市军管会负责人"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c43643869f","type":"title","text":"北京市军事管制委员会负责人谈取缔一切反动组织","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"49cd4789b2","type":"paragraph","text":"根据中共中央，国务院2·12号通知第二条（对组织采取的办法）有九个组织不是好组织，应该宣布取缔，有三个反动组织。不是好组织嘛，就是坏组织，反动的有三个。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"20e23f4f42","type":"paragraph","text":"1．全国灭资军造反团总部。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aba2e2035c","type":"paragraph","text":"2．全国国营农场红色造反兵团。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"37accea795","type":"paragraph","text":"3．全国上山下乡知识青年捍卫真理革命造反团。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e97083719","type":"paragraph","text":"4．全国军垦战士革命造反团。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7a1c3dff14","type":"paragraph","text":"5．国际红卫军中国支队。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22aab714bf","type":"paragraph","text":"6．全国红色劳动者造反总团，简称“全红总”。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa812dac2c","type":"paragraph","text":"7．全国上山下乡知识青年红色革命造反团。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"558e0ac24c","type":"paragraph","text":"8．全国上山下乡知识青年红色第一线战斗队。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"af0c00db8e","type":"paragraph","text":"9．全国聋人革命造反联络总部。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2f7b0b2e42","type":"paragraph","text":"第一个，第二个，第六个，这是三个反动组织。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a65c6f8eef","type":"paragraph","text":"从他们成立以来，在北京活动的共同特点有以下几点：","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d857d5f7ee","type":"paragraph","text":"1．组织本身就是坏的，是坏人组成的，是社会渣滓组成的，地、富、反、坏、右；流氓、临时工、合同工中的一些渣滓。总的来说就是坏人。","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b7224a2787","type":"paragraph","text":"2．破坏文化大革命，矛头指向中央文革，指向毛主席。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d25d4e82a1","type":"paragraph","text":"3．大搞经济主义。","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a0894731e7","type":"paragraph","text":"4．挑动群众搞武斗。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bb559234ee","type":"paragraph","text":"5．抢劫、霸占。","index":17,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22bea3fa34","type":"paragraph","text":"6．伙同一些坏人冲中南海。","index":18,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"883cc1e1d4","type":"paragraph","text":"7．严重破坏国家财产。","index":19,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5661d6e7ea","type":"paragraph","text":"8．乱搞男女关系、强奸、甚至轮奸。","index":20,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0415cd4ca7","type":"paragraph","text":"三个反动组织的主要事情，一个一个地介绍如下：","index":21,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"bd863e504a","type":"paragraph","text":"1．全国灭资军造反团总部。","index":22,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1e52a49c72","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）是坏人组成的，地、富、反、坏、右。","index":23,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd58e5a7c3","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）长权霸占国家房子。","index":24,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4fa3edeef5","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）伙同坏人冲中南海。","index":25,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b9e8febdfe","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）大搞经济主义。","index":26,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"043adb2075","type":"paragraph","text":"2．全国国营农场红色造反兵团。","index":27,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f04d9d472d","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）公开集会反对《人民日报》“抓革命，促生产”的宣传。","index":28,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f64d0b450","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）与劳改犯一起冲中南海。","index":29,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e36aac2dc","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）奸污妇女。","index":30,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"443fa79dd6","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）大搞经济主义。","index":31,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a263eda1be","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）严重破坏国家财产。","index":32,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"00b291730d","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）挑动武斗。","index":33,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6f853b7303","type":"paragraph","text":"3．“全红总”，头头是王振海。","index":34,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"94feebb488","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）它的组成是临时工、合同工里面的坏人，它到处造谣撞骗，说中央承认自己了。","index":35,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"667b8ed1b8","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）煽动一些人到北京市胡闹，在全国各地招来一些人到北京取闹。","index":36,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f4038b060e","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）大搞经济主义。","index":37,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fee996fe03","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）冲国务院接待站，绑架工作人员。","index":38,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"7b1edf3ead","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）积极为五类分子翻案。","index":39,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c1d8bfde03","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）以中央名义发通告，发到全国；私自与外国人开座谈会，大肆诬蔑社会主义制度。他们的后台据说是国民党少将。根据调查他们昨天晚上还在开会。","index":40,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6dfcee9e8","type":"paragraph","text":"（以上是传达记录）","index":41,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0b788afd0e","type":"paragraph","text":"谁反对毛主席就打倒谁！谁反对中央文革谁就是反革命！","index":42,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"05152f8db3","type":"paragraph","text":"用鲜血和生命保卫毛主席、保卫中央文革！","index":43,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"377972a26b","type":"paragraph","text":"誓死和中央文革战斗在一起，胜利在一起！","index":44,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"cc6da44b02","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国灭资军造反团总部！","index":45,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"13b589a104","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国国营农场红色造反兵团！","index":46,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e16ccf40b","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒全国红色劳动者造反总团！","index":47,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"65c2f4eb10","type":"paragraph","text":"打倒一切反革命组织！","index":48,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"22732bc9a3","type":"paragraph","text":"敌人不投降，就叫他灭亡！","index":49,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"007b7ec0a8","type":"paragraph","text":"无产阶级专政万岁！","index":50,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4d255bb7bd","type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的中国共产党万岁！","index":51,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"09e9fe7c64","type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的导师，伟大的领袖、伟大的统帅、伟大的舵手毛主席万岁！万岁！万万、岁！","index":52,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"71ae6d118b","type":"paragraph","text":"中国科学院红卫兵革命造反司令部","index":53,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d5ddee6052","type":"paragraph","text":"1967年2月25日印","index":54,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"560961f44a","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}